The paper deals with pilot design in multi-cell Massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also involves optimization techniques (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG) to solve the non-convex problem. Finally, the paper specifically mentions Massive MIMO (cs.MM) as the system under consideration.
